THE RIGHT PLACE AND
THE RIGHT TIME?

33
00:02:00,333 --> 00:02:02,416
WELL, IT DOESN'T EXIST.
YOU HAVE TO CREATE IT.

34
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,708
- LOOK, I REALLY DON'T WANT TO
TALK ABOUT THIS WITH YOU.

35
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:06,041
- JUST LISTEN!

36
00:02:06,125 --> 00:02:08,333
- NO, YOU LISTEN! WE'RE
GOING AT OUR OWN PACE.

37
00:02:08,416 --> 00:02:09,750
WE DON'T NEED YOUR HELP!

38
00:02:09,833 --> 00:02:13,166
- WELL, THIS SOUNDS LIKE
EXCITING LUNCHTIME CONVERSATION.

39
00:02:13,250 --> 00:02:15,916
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS TALKING ABOUT?
AM I ALLOWED TO KNOW?

40
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,416
- YEAH. YOU'RE A GIRL.
MAYBE YOU CAN TALK TO HIM.

41
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:20,291
- HUH? WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

42
00:02:20,375 --> 00:02:21,916
- YAMATO WANTED TO
GET IT ON WITH SAKURAI

43
