44
00:02:23,291 --> 00:02:24,875
- WHAT? NO I DIDN'T!

45
00:02:24,958 --> 00:02:26,833
- UH...

46
00:02:26,916 --> 00:02:28,250
- I WAS TRYING TO EXPLAIN TO
HIM THAT THE ATMOSPHERE

47
00:02:28,333 --> 00:02:30,000
