56
00:02:48,833 --> 00:02:51,875
- THAT'S NOT TRUE. YOU'RE THE
ONLY ONE THAT THINKS THAT!

57
00:02:51,958 --> 00:02:54,875
- COME ON, AKITSUKI! LET'S GO!
STUPIDITY'S CONTAGIOUS!

58
00:02:54,958 --> 00:02:57,708
- YAMATO AND I AREN'T DONE
TALKING, YET!

59
00:02:57,791 --> 00:02:59,916
- JUST LEAVE ME ALONE. PLEASE!

60
00:03:14,083 --> 00:03:16,166
- Soichi: OK, GUYS, WE'RE DONE.

61
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:17,708
- ( Yamato grunting )

62
00:03:20,833 --> 00:03:23,708
- HEY, AKITSUKI. GOOD WORK
TODAY. THAT LOOKS HEAVY.

63
00:03:23,791 --> 00:03:25,166
