64
00:03:25,250 --> 00:03:27,750
- WELL, SURE.
IT'S PRETTY EASY NOW.

65
00:03:27,833 --> 00:03:29,541
- Kinugasa: IT LOOKS
EASY ENOUGH.

66
00:03:32,166 --> 00:03:34,041
- GREAT. IT'S OUR FORMER
CAPTAIN AGAIN.

67
00:03:34,125 --> 00:03:36,166
- OKAY.

68
00:03:36,250 --> 00:03:37,750
UNFORTUNATELY, YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
TO BUILD UP A LOT MORE MUSCLE

69
