THREE SETS TO YOUR ROUTINE.

71
00:03:42,083 --> 00:03:43,583
- WHAT? NO WAY!

72
00:03:43,666 --> 00:03:45,583
- HUH? WHAT WAS THAT?

73
00:03:45,666 --> 00:03:49,000
- AH! I SAID I'LL DO IT. I'LL DO
IT, OKAY? PLEASE LET ME DO IT.

74
00:03:49,083 --> 00:03:50,708
- YOU GOT IT!
- I'M BEGGING YOU!

75
00:03:50,791 --> 00:03:52,791
- ALL RIGHT, YOU BETTER
WORK HARD NOW.

76
00:03:53,916 --> 00:03:55,125
- WHAT WAS THAT FOR?

77
00:03:55,208 --> 00:03:57,000
- UM, AKITSUKI?

78
00:03:57,083 --> 00:03:59,291
I HAVE SOMETHING TO DO
TODAY SO I CAN'T STAY.

79
00:03:59,375 --> 00:04:00,500
IS THAT OKAY WITH YOU?

80
00:04:00,583 --> 00:04:02,291
- YEAH, THAT'S FINE.
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

81
00:04:02,375 --> 00:04:05,875
IF YOU NEED TO GO, GO AHEAD.

82
00:04:05,958 --> 00:04:08,458
- IT'S RAINING OUTSIDE.
I BET YOU DIDN'T BRING

83
