CAKES DON'T TASTE AS GOOD
WHEN I EAT THEM ALONE, ANYWAY.

101
00:04:53,916 --> 00:04:55,708
- YEAH, BUT I ALREADY TOLD
YOU I DON'T REALLY FEEL LIKE

102
00:04:55,791 --> 00:04:57,250
CAKE RIGHT NOW, REMEMBER?

103
00:04:57,333 --> 00:05:00,250
- OH STOP. THIS IS THE ONLY
TIME YOU CAN HAVE THEM!

104
00:05:00,333 --> 00:05:01,958
- ( grunting )

105
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,666
- ALL RIGHT, JUST TWO MORE SETS.

106
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:09,333
- DON'T GIVE UP!

107
00:05:09,416 --> 00:05:10,791
- I'M NOT.

108
00:05:10,875 --> 00:05:13,291
THIS IS SO AWKWARD.

109
00:05:13,375 --> 00:05:15,041
- Miki: WHAT?
DO YOU MEAN TO TELL ME

110
00:05:15,125 --> 00:05:18,125
