YOUR BAG THIS WHOLE TIME?

111
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:20,375
- THAT'S RIGHT. I'M SORRY.

112
00:05:20,458 --> 00:05:22,041
I DIDN'T REALIZE I HADN'T
ALREADY CHECKED IT.

113
00:05:22,125 --> 00:05:24,291
- YOU'RE REALLY STARTING
TO LOSE YOUR FOCUS.

114
00:05:24,375 --> 00:05:28,000
BUT NEVER MIND, I'M GLAD YOU
FOUND IT. LET'S GO EAT, 'KAY?

115
00:05:28,083 --> 00:05:29,833
- WELL...

116
00:05:29,916 --> 00:05:31,750
I CAN'T. I FORGOT I
HAVE TO WRITE A REPORT.

117
00:05:31,833 --> 00:05:33,583
IT'S DUE TODAY, SO...

118
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:34,833
- ARE YOU KIDDING?

119
00:05:34,916 --> 00:05:37,125
- NOPE. I REALLY NEED TO
FINISH IT BEFORE I GO.

120
00:05:37,208 --> 00:05:40,083
- OH, COME ON. YOU CAN PUT IT
OFF FOR JUST A LITTLE WHILE.

121
00:05:40,166 --> 00:05:42,333
- I CAN'T!
MY TEACHER WILL KILL ME!

122
00:05:42,416 --> 00:05:46,708
- OKAY, OKAY, FINE.
I'LL JUST GO BY MYSELF.

123
00:05:46,791 --> 00:05:49,250
- MAN, I'M SO GLAD THAT'S OVER.

124
00:05:53,666 --> 00:05:56,000
HEY, GUYS. I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU HAVEN'T LEFT YET.

125
00:05:56,083 --> 00:05:57,416
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

126
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:58,916
- JUST HANGING OUT!

127
00:06:01,875 --> 00:06:04,625
- OH GREAT.
NOW IT'S RAINING HARDER.

128
00:06:04,708 --> 00:06:07,916
OH WELL, I GUESS
I NEED TO CALL MIHO.

129
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,750
- WAIT, DON'T CALL HER YET.

130
00:06:12,041 --> 00:06:13,125
