138
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,000
- OKAY.

139
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:40,708
WELL, THANKS.
THAT'S VERY NICE OF YOU.

140
00:06:40,791 --> 00:06:41,916
- SURE.

141
00:06:43,458 --> 00:06:44,625
- SEE YA!

142
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:57,041
- UH, SUZUKA?

143
00:06:58,416 --> 00:07:01,833
