FOR AKITSUKI?

144
00:07:04,208 --> 00:07:06,125
- WHY WOULD YOU
ASK ME THAT QUESTION?

145
00:07:06,208 --> 00:07:09,041
- WELL, IT'S BECAUSE YOU'VE
ACTED KIND OF STRANGE

146
00:07:09,125 --> 00:07:11,333
EVER SINCE YOU GOT BACK
FROM HIROSHIMA.

147
00:07:11,416 --> 00:07:14,125
AND JUST NOW IT REALLY SEEMED
LIKE YOU WERE WAITING FOR HIM

148
00:07:14,208 --> 00:07:16,250
SO THAT YOU COULD
GO HOME TOGETHER.

149
00:07:16,333 --> 00:07:18,000
- NO, THAT'S NOT IT.

150
00:07:20,416 --> 00:07:22,958
