LIKE THAT. DON'T BE SILLY!

152
00:07:29,708 --> 00:07:31,958
- I SEE. I DIDN'T REALLY THINK
YOU FELT THAT WAY.

153
00:07:32,041 --> 00:07:33,416
- LET'S GO, MIKI.

154
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:35,625
CAKE IS STARTING TO SOUND
REALLY GOOD ALL OF A SUDDEN.

155
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:40,708
- WELL ALL RIGHT THEN,
EVERYTHING IS ON ME TODAY,

156
00:07:40,791 --> 00:07:42,500
SO EAT AS MUCH CAKE AS YOU WANT!

157
00:07:42,583 --> 00:07:44,083
- MIKI...

158
00:07:44,166 --> 00:07:45,333
- 'KAY?

159
00:07:46,291 --> 00:07:47,708
- OKAY. THANKS.

160
00:07:54,791 --> 00:07:56,583
- ( whistle blowing )

161
00:07:56,666 --> 00:07:59,375
- OKAY! THAT'S IT FOR TODAY!
DON'T FORGET TO COOL DOWN!

162
00:08:00,375 --> 00:08:01,708
