00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:22,333
- AKITSUKI AND SAKURAI SEEM TO
BE PRETTY CLOSE THESE DAYS.

169
00:08:22,416 --> 00:08:23,458
- WELL OF COURSE THEY ARE.

170
00:08:23,541 --> 00:08:25,666
