181
00:08:50,166 --> 00:08:51,500
- OH, RIGHT.

182
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:58,291
- I REALLY DON'T GET
KINUGASA SEMPAI.

183
00:08:58,375 --> 00:09:00,666
