THAT STRICT WITH ME?

184
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,666
- BECAUSE HE BELIEVES IN YOU.

185
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:04,291
- I GUESS.

186
00:09:04,375 --> 00:09:07,708
- Nana: NANA'S SONGS ARE ONLY
PLAYED IN HIGH QUALITY AUDIO!

187
00:09:07,791 --> 00:09:10,750
( Nana singing )
♪ BABY I'VE BEEN GOING CRAZY ♪

188
00:09:10,833 --> 00:09:12,875
- WOW. THAT'S COOL.

189
00:09:12,958 --> 00:09:14,500
- ♪ I LOVE YOU ♪

190
00:09:14,583 --> 00:09:16,208
♪ YES, I ADORE YOU ♪

191
00:09:16,291 --> 00:09:19,041
- ARE YOU ATTRACTED
TO NANA SHIRAKAWA?

192
00:09:19,125 --> 00:09:21,208
- OH, NO, NOT AT ALL.

193
00:09:21,291 --> 00:09:22,458
I WAS JUST THINKING
ABOUT BUYING

194
00:09:22,541 --> 00:09:25,166
ONE OF THOSE REALLY
COOL MD PLAYERS!

195
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:26,500
- YOU WERE?

196
00:09:26,583 --> 00:09:28,000
- YEAH. I PROMISE!

197
00:09:28,083 --> 00:09:31,125
BUT THEY'RE SO DARN EXPENSIVE.
I COULDN'T AFFORD IT.

198
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,958
- I SEE.

199
00:09:38,541 --> 00:09:40,041
- Waitress: WELL, HELLO THERE!

200
00:09:45,041 --> 00:09:46,541
HOW ARE YOU, TODAY?

201
00:09:47,666 --> 00:09:50,083
- WHAT'S THE MATTER, HONOKA?
- HUH?

202
00:09:50,166 --> 00:09:52,875
I NOTICED YOU SEEM A LITTLE
UNEASY TODAY.

203
00:09:52,958 --> 00:09:54,666
- NO. WELL, MAYBE A LITTLE.

204
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:57,083
I'VE BEEN TALKING ABOUT YOU
A LOT TO A FRIEND OF MINE,

205
00:09:57,166 --> 00:09:59,208
AND SHE REALLY WANTS TO
MEET YOU TODAY.

206
00:09:59,291 --> 00:10:01,250
- WHAT? SHE DOES?

207
00:10:01,333 --> 00:10:03,625
- MMM-HMM. I SENT HER
AN EMAIL AFTER PRACTICE

208
00:10:03,708 --> 00:10:06,041
AND TOLD HER WE GOT OUT EARLY,
SO SHE'S ON HER WAY RIGHT NOW.

209
00:10:06,125 --> 00:10:08,875
- OKAY. THAT'S WHY
YOU'RE SO JITTERY.

210
00:10:08,958 --> 00:10:11,166
- I'M SORRY. I KNOW
THIS IS REALLY SUDDEN

211
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:12,666
AND I DON'T MEAN TO TROUBLE YOU.

212
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:14,125
PLEASE FORGIVE ME?

213
00:10:14,208 --> 00:10:16,958
- OH, DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
IT'S NO TROUBLE AT ALL.

214
00:10:17,041 --> 00:10:19,041
BUT, UM, DO I LOOK OKAY?

215
00:10:19,125 --> 00:10:20,375
- THERE YOU ARE!

216
00:10:22,625 --> 00:10:25,916
I JUST GOT OUT OF WORK. I HOPE
YOU WEREN'T WAITING TOO LONG!

217
00:10:27,791 --> 00:10:28,916
- OH MY GOSH.

218
00:10:31,166 --> 00:10:32,458
OH MY GOSH!

219
00:10:32,541 --> 00:10:36,208
- SO, THIS IS YOUR BOYFRIEND?
HE'S REALLY CUTE!

220
00:10:36,291 --> 00:10:38,500
- SHOULDN'T YOU BE WEARING A
DISGUISE OR SOMETHING, NANA?

221
00:10:38,583 --> 00:10:39,833
YOU NEED TO BE CAREFUL!

222
00:10:39,916 --> 00:10:41,708
- NAH, IT'S TOO MUCH TROUBLE!

223
00:10:41,791 --> 00:10:45,125
- WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME
YOUR FRIEND WAS HER?

224
00:10:45,208 --> 00:10:47,083
- SO, ARE YOU SURPRISED?

225
00:10:47,166 --> 00:10:49,750
I'M NANA SHIRAKAWA.
NICE TO MEET YOU!

226
00:10:49,833 --> 00:10:52,125
- UH, YEAH, VERY NICE
TO MEET YOU, TOO!

227
00:10:52,208 --> 00:10:56,083
I'M A BIG FAN!
I JUST LOVE YOUR TV SHOW!

228
00:10:56,166 --> 00:10:57,750
- I DON'T HAVE A TV SHOW.

229
00:10:57,833 --> 00:10:59,291
- OH YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT!

230
00:10:59,375 --> 00:11:02,041
- I'M SORRY, I GUESS YOU'RE
A LITTLE STARTLED, HUH?

231
00:11:02,916 --> 00:11:04,500
- MAYBE A LITTLE.

232
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:06,916
- OH, MY GOSH. IT'S...
IT REALLY IS HER!

233
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,833
- EVERYONE'S STARING.

234
00:11:08,916 --> 00:11:10,333
- WELL THEN,
LET'S GO SOMEWHERE ELSE!

235
00:11:13,875 --> 00:11:16,625
- WOW. SO YOU TWO HAVE BEEN
FRIENDS SINCE JUNIOR HIGH?

236
00:11:16,708 --> 00:11:18,125
- UM, YEAH.

237
00:11:18,208 --> 00:11:20,958
- YEP. I GUESS YOU COULD SAY
WE'RE BEST FRIENDS, RIGHT?

238
00:11:21,041 --> 00:11:23,250
