TREATED ME SO STRANGELY

239
00:11:23,333 --> 00:11:26,166
BECAUSE OF MY CAREER. EVERYONE
ELSE WAS SO AFRAID TO TALK

240
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:28,541
TO ME, THEY MADE ME FEEL
LIKE SOME KIND OF FREAK.

241
00:11:28,625 --> 00:11:30,208
