TRYING TO BE MEAN TO ME,

242
00:11:30,291 --> 00:11:33,541
BUT I REALLY DIDN'T HAVE
ANY FRIENDS AT ALL.

243
00:11:33,625 --> 00:11:36,833
- I'M SORRY, I GUESS SHOW
BUSINESS GETS PRETTY ROUGH, HUH?

244
00:11:36,916 --> 00:11:38,916
- MMM-HMM.

245
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,833
ONE DAY, I HAD A REALLY
HORRIBLE TIME AT SCHOOL

246
00:11:40,916 --> 00:11:42,791
AND DESPERATELY
NEEDED A CIGARETTE.

247
00:11:42,875 --> 00:11:44,541
I STOPPED AT THE INARI
SHRINE TO LIGHT UP

248
00:11:44,625 --> 00:11:46,583
ON MY WAY HOME FROM CLASS.

249
00:11:53,416 --> 00:11:54,791
AND THAT'S WHEN
THE SHRINE MAIDEN

250
00:11:54,875 --> 00:11:57,083
WHO WORKED THERE APPROACHED ME.

251
00:11:57,166 --> 00:11:59,666
- YOU KNOW, YOU SHOULDN'T SMOKE.
IT'S REALLY BAD FOR YOU.

252
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,416
- WHAT? JUST LEAVE ME ALONE.

253
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,916
- I'M SORRY, I CAN'T.

254
