SO, WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

255
00:12:06,666 --> 00:12:08,541
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
YOU DON'T KNOW WHO I AM?

256
00:12:08,625 --> 00:12:10,583
- THAT'S WHY I ASKED
WHAT YOUR NAME WAS.

257
00:12:10,666 --> 00:12:14,166
- I THINK SHE INSULTED MY PRIDE
MORE THAN ANYTHING ELSE.

258
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:17,625
