LISTEN TO SOME BOSSY COSPLAYER!

259
00:12:17,708 --> 00:12:20,500
- WHAT? THIS ISN'T A COSPLAY!
I WORK HERE!

260
00:12:20,583 --> 00:12:22,625
HOW RUDE!
