274
00:12:47,375 --> 00:12:48,708
- SO DON'T GO AROUND
TRYING TO FORCE YOURSELF

275
00:12:48,791 --> 00:12:50,583
ON HER. IT'S NOT COOL!

276
00:12:50,666 --> 00:12:53,000
