ANYTHING ELSE BEFORE.

345
00:15:54,083 --> 00:15:55,875
ARE YOU TONE-DEAF OR SOMETHING?

346
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:00,541
- I CAN SING.
JUST GIVE ME A SECOND.

347
00:16:00,625 --> 00:16:02,750
