YOUR BEST, AKITSUKI.

348
00:16:02,833 --> 00:16:05,583
- I'M NOT JUST GONNA SIT HERE
AND LET HER CALL ME TONE-DEAF.

349
00:16:05,666 --> 00:16:07,041
