350
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:10,416
HERE IT IS.

351
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:13,166
- Suzuka: YAMATO, YOU CAN'T SING
THAT. THAT'S THE ONE I PICKED.

352
00:16:13,250 --> 00:16:14,833
