ANOTHER ONE THEN.

355
00:16:17,958 --> 00:16:20,375
- OH, JUST MAKE IT
A DUET AND SING!

356
00:16:22,333 --> 00:16:24,416
- I DON'T KNOW.
I GUESS WE COULD DO THAT.

357
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:27,250
