YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

367
00:17:02,208 --> 00:17:04,083
- I SWORE I WASN'T GOING
TO DO ANYTHING

368
00:17:04,166 --> 00:17:06,666
TO HURT HONOKA'S
FEELINGS ANYMORE.

369
00:17:13,916 --> 00:17:16,208
- MAN! I SANG SO MUCH!

370
00:17:16,291 --> 00:17:17,416
- THAT WAS FUN!

371
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,125
- WELL, SUZUKA AND I STILL
HAVE STUFF TO DO

372
00:17:19,208 --> 00:17:20,375
BEFORE WE HAVE TO GO HOME.

373
00:17:20,458 --> 00:17:21,666
- OKAY.

